{"tid":1555272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者再次成功光復上水","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T18:36:43.000Z","uid":51271,"like":703,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"afdae4e419e0ed199bc60204959a2f9d09decb64","tid":1555272,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LAMTSZKINGOFFICIALPAGE/photos/pcb.697759850725849/697759494059218/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLAMTSZKINGOFFICIALPAGE%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.697759850725849%2F697759494059218%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bui3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=2271d600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LAMTSZKINGOFFICIALPAGE/photos/pcb.697759850725849/697759494059218/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n林子琼 LAM TSZ KING<br />\n5 mins &middot;<br />\n<br />\n17:43 上水即時<br />\n<br />\n平時打爆電話都唔肯黎清水貨，一話要光復上水你地就仆出黎趕。<br />\n<br />\n18個軍裝警，見到我地 林卓廷 LAM CHEUK TING Kwok Long Fung 郭㙟豐 一黎，即刻上車撤離。<br />\n<br />\n事實證明趕水貨唔係趕唔到，係你地唔肯去趕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70648126_697759520725882_8991643398590955520_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGDKWXlUMvIDplso9-fT3U7dMAJGk873YKA8qaXfJWwSVFZwjjUq7DTyip3p88xoKC96R_hnugHMlNbddSkXe1c2E5hnfoMJKB7K0W4Mqmg2w&amp;_nc_oc=AQleXw69W6k9SBIFtCRiQi5VOZMnaVT0L5cET0cDXM7_xIrlXl8s2nJJq06allvIKDc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=79cf68a8f58b66d5c094557cb52f39c1&amp;oe=5E015F3B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70648126_697759520725882_8991643398590955520_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_eui2%3DAeGDKWXlUMvIDplso9-fT3U7dMAJGk873YKA8qaXfJWwSVFZwjjUq7DTyip3p88xoKC96R_hnugHMlNbddSkXe1c2E5hnfoMJKB7K0W4Mqmg2w%26_nc_oc%3DAQleXw69W6k9SBIFtCRiQi5VOZMnaVT0L5cET0cDXM7_xIrlXl8s2nJJq06allvIKDc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D79cf68a8f58b66d5c094557cb52f39c1%26oe%3