5272,"uid":56323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d3863f87ba5fc1a75edfa01ff9f8ef658a6e041","tid":1555272,"uid":9328,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"話唔定D高層根本有利益輸送, 不過都無人去查, ICAC貪埋一份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"ICAC我信班人冇貪<br />\n但一早比人廢撚左, 都係冇撚用<br />\n成班人等退休, 人工福利又少過其他紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d87167002add29e817f1be145bd1e9013bf867","tid":1555272,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f9499d2e13f72916da7eb942a3f7d417cb4eb9","tid":1555272,"uid":304321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:50:39.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n建議呢個星期全力重建連儂牆<br />\n914 915 遊行要去，但完左就起返連儂牆<br />\n而唔係衝擊或散水或轉場<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">等所有人知道發生緊咩事先！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">連儂牆起源於反共，呢條戰線不能倒！</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點吶喊</span>！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bui3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=7d05ba64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"339a0fcc1242272328092e070fbacd55bec1245b","tid":1555272,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9a6d68561f0c2c4939cec8fde561ef973da160","tid":1555272,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff17222d112aebd05babd9f791a2fef0a220c805","tid":1555272,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b653c0faf45e44537f2c35facfe